   - **Generative AI** continues to dominate with applications ranging from creative industries (art, music, writing) to technical fields (data analysis, software development).
   - **AI Integration** in businesses, including customer service (chatbots, virtual assistants), healthcare (AI diagnostics, personalized treatment), and logistics (AI-driven supply chains).
